The paper deals with the application of deep learning and machine learning techniques for the automatic detection of pathologies in fundus photographs. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of unsupervised probabilistic models, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of these techniques is in the field of medical imaging (cs.MED) and information retrieval (cs.IR) for decision support.
